Toyota Fortuner G 2.7. First owner. Immaculate condition. Bumper to bumper original. Not even a single scratch on it. Multiple upgrades installed.

Price of PPF and Top vinyl is 250,000
4. Original 3M anti glare full visibility window tints CR70 installed on all windows with ultimate heat Rejection. Worth 40k. 
5. High quality fabric seat covers with quilting. 
6. Leather cover for Steering wheel. Hand stitched. 
7. Vip number. Islamabad registered. 

Car is sparingly used as a 3rd car. Only used for a few trips to lahore and islamabad. Condition of the car speaks for itself. Its only 11k driven. 

Reason to sell upgrading to next model. Not in a hurry to sell. Price is very slightly negotiable. Polite No to low ballers and dealers. Car will be sold as is where is. Only contact if you are a serious buyer and understand the car and its expensive high quality upgrades and situation of car availability and existing own situation in the market. Will not be sold to dealers and owner will have to get the car transferred to their own name within 15 days. 
Please call within office hours and its better to text before calling. I repeat price is firm. So please only call if u agree to the written price. Otherwise there are other ADs where you can try your luck. Leave a message if i dont take the call. I will call back.
